that everyone in this school

31:20.208 --> 31:21.475
understood what it was like

31:21.509 --> 31:22.976
to see the world
from this chair,

31:23.011 --> 31:25.245
and he helped me see
all that I could be

31:25.279 --> 31:26.546
even though I was in it.

31:26.581 --> 31:28.148
He is the most genuine...

31:28.182 --> 31:29.683
honest...
...kind...

31:29.717 --> 31:31.852
generous...
...sand dollar...

31:33.588 --> 31:36.323
amazing man any of us
have ever met.

31:36.357 --> 31:40.394
He loved and looked
after every one of us

31:40.428 --> 31:42.796
