36:13.215 --> 36:15.216
She actually won.

36:19.826 --> 36:21.866
You guys, you're gonna
miss my big moment.

36:21.891 --> 36:24.125
Get your butts
to the auditorium.

36:25.659 --> 36:28.139
Hang on a second.

36:28.164 --> 36:31.566
Sue Sylvester didn't win.

36:31.600 --> 36:33.435
Maybe she took away Glee Club,

36:33.469 --> 36:35.937
but she'll never
take away what we had.

36:35.971 --> 36:38.640
We were part
of something incredible.

36:38.674 --> 36:39.974
It was more than that.

36:40.009 --> 36:41.543
You know, we helped
each other become

36:41.577 --> 36:44.279
better people in this room.

36:44.313 --> 36:47.115
No one can ever
take that away from us.

36:47.149 --> 36:48.383
