something's going to change it.</i>

42:07.637 --> 42:09.717
<i>Being a part of something</i>
<i>special makes you</i>

42:09.739 --> 42:12.207
- <i>special, right?</i> - PUCK: <i> I was
tossing kids into Dumpsters.</i>

42:12.241 --> 42:13.875
ARTIE: <i> I had never
kissed a girl before.</i>

42:13.910 --> 42:15.577
KURT: <i> I wasn't honest
about who I was.</i>

42:15.611 --> 42:17.379
Five...

42:17.413 --> 42:21.116
MERCEDES: <i> And Glee Club will
never end, Mr. Shue, because</i>

42:21.150 --> 42:22.951
<i>you</i> are <i> Glee Club.</i>

42:24.744 --> 42:26.464
