<i>'Cause in this room</i>

42:26.489 --> 42:28.557
<i>it doesn't matter</i>
<i>if you're gay or straight.</i>

42:28.591 --> 42:29.791
<i>What matters is that</i>
<i>we're friends.</i>

42:29.825 --> 42:32.194
SANTANA:
<i>The struggle continues, but...</i>

42:32.228 --> 42:33.895
<i>at least I know I'm not alone.</i>

42:33.930 --> 42:36.364
RACHEL: <i> If I'd let you down
when you needed me the most,</i>

42:36.399 --> 42:39.598
<i>I'd never forgive myself.</i>

42:39.632 --> 42:41.466
FINN: <i> We went around the
room and everybody said</i>

42:41.500 --> 42:43.134
<i>what they wanted</i>
<i>to win this thing for,</i>

42:43.168 --> 42:44.736
<i>and we all said the same thing.</i>

42:44.770 --> 42:46.504
<i>We want to win this for you.</i>

